if I have another baby.

00:22.837 --> 00:24.737
Well, I wish that you
had never told me that.

00:24.772 --> 00:27.740
I know you won't
tell Ben or anyone else.

00:27.775 --> 00:30.777
You are the photo
on Tom Bowman's desk.

00:30.811 --> 00:32.812
Oh, God.
You're Milton, aren't you?

00:32.847 --> 00:35.715
Daniel. Grace is upstairs.
She is on restriction.

00:35.749 --> 00:37.784
Well, I think I just saw Grace
sneak behind your back.

00:37.818 --> 00:39.619
<i>I saw</i>
<i>Daniel go in the house.</i>

00:39.653 --> 00:41.688
Go down there and quietly
tell him I'm waiting for him.

00:42.823 --> 00:44.390
I don't think so.

00:44.425 --> 00:45.859
I did talk
to Admissions

00:45.893 --> 00:48.494
<i>and unfortunately they're
not going to accept you.</i>

00:48.529 --> 00:50.530
She said you tried
to have sex with her.

00:51.799 --> 00:52.866
Ricky!

00:52.900 --> 00:54.634
I thought about
all we've been through

00:54.668 --> 00:56.769
