at your stupid sign.

02:22.456 --> 02:25.358
If we're going to do this, we might
as well do the best job we can.

02:25.392 --> 02:27.794
I mean, how many people
can say they've done this?

02:27.828 --> 02:29.462
I don't think
I'd admit to it.

02:29.496 --> 02:30.596
