to leave it alone.

03:51.445 --> 03:52.678
Wait, then where
did you go that night?

03:52.713 --> 03:55.515
I just went for a walk.
I just walked it off.

03:55.549 --> 03:57.717
I didn't go anywhere. I just didn't
want to tell you about this.

03:57.751 --> 03:59.352
Because?

03:59.386 --> 04:00.553
